Slingshot
===============================

There is a package for Oneiric and Natty (not supported) in Elementary Unstable-Upstream PPA:
$ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:elementaryart/unstable-upstream
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install slingshot-launcher

This package is automatically updated everyday.

===============================

You can also compile Slingshot from source.
You need the following dependencies (on Ubuntu/Debian):
 -  cmake,
 -  pkg-config,
 -  valac (>= 0.12.0),
 -  libgtk-3-dev,
 -  libgranite-dev,
 -  libgee-dev,
 -  libgnome-menu-dev,
 -  libzeitgeist-dev
then:
$ mkdir build
$ cd build/
$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ make
$ sudo make install

===============================

